title: Output not showing on A Tour of Go's Maps Exercises
body:
by **guilherme.mpaes**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Go to Maps Exercise
2. Comment the wc.Test line
3. Insert any fmt.Println("test") kind of statement on main()

What is the expected output?
The output show be shown on the Output section

What do you see instead?
The output is not shown

Which compiler are you using (5g, 6g, 8g, gccgo)?
A Tour of Go's compiler
